# package.json Changes for Jest to Vitest Migration

## Scripts Section

### Before
```json
{
  "scripts": {
    "test": "jest --config ./test/config/jest.config.js",
    "test:watch": "jest --watch --config ./test/config/jest.config.js",
    "test:cov": "jest --coverage --config ./test/config/jest.config.js",
    "test:debug": "node --inspect-brk -r tsconfig-paths/register -r ts-node/register node_modules/.bin/jest --runInBand",
    "test:ci": "jest --forceExit --config ./test/config/jest.config.ci.js && cat ./coverage-ci/lcov.info",
    "test:ci:no:coverage": "jest --forceExit --config ./test/config/jest.config.ci.nocov.js"
  }
}
```

### After
```json
{
  "scripts": {
    "test": "vitest run",
    "test:watch": "vitest",
    "test:cov": "vitest run --coverage",
    "test:debug": "vitest --inspect-brk",
    "test:ci": "vitest run --coverage && cat ./coverage-ci/lcov.info",
    "test:ci:no:coverage": "vitest run"
  }
}
```

